    <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;Legend&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;━━  MQTT publish/subscribe (pub/sub, broker-mediated)&lt;br/&gt;┄┄  CoAP request/response (RESTful, UDP/DTLS)&lt;br/&gt;QoS 0 = fire and forget · QoS 1 = at least once · QoS 2 = exactly once&lt;br/&gt;CBOR = Concise Binary Object Representation (compact binary payload)" style="rounded=1;arcSize=6;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#B4B2A9;fontColor=#5F5E5A;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1">
